Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:16.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 무예자들도 승리와 영광을 꿈꾸며 떨쳐 일어나고 있었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:16.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Martial Artists take part in these battles, dreaming of victory and honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:23.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 지금, 카라쿠리 무예자 제일을 꿈꾸는 터무니없는 영웅이 탄생했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:23.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,And now, a wild hero has arrived, who wants to be the number one Karakuri Martial Artist!
