Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:01:00.96,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,A skilled Martial Artist wanders Jipangu Country
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:06.59,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,그 이름은 카라쿠리인 무사시
