Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:39.62,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,싸우는 한껏 고요함과 함께
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:39.62,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight your hardest with tranquility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.88,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,무예! 이도류 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.88,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Art! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:51.09,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,미간이 빛나고 있었다 무사시!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:51.09,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Shining brow! Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:05.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵は卑弥呼と名乗る絶世の美女と会い、武芸大会に出場した。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:05.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 히미코라고 하는 절세의 미녀하고 만나 무예 대회에 출전했다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:05.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi met a rare beauty named Himiko, and participated in a martial arts contest.
Comment: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、それは不知火一族が無での辰手先を集めるために開いたものだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 그것은 시라누이 일족이 실력 좋은 부하를 모으기 위해 연 것이었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:11.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,But the purpose of the contest was to gather capable subordinates for Shiranui Clan.
Comment: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うしわかに事実を聞かされた武蔵は、大会をめちゃめちゃにしてしまう。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우시와카에게 사실을 들은 무사시는 대회를 엉망진창으로 만들고 만다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:17.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,After hearing about the truth from Ushiwaka, Musashi made a mess of the contest.
Comment: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.17,TitleEP,ja,0,0,0,,げ⁉おちこみコジローだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.17,TitleEP,ko,0,0,233,,어!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.17,TitleEP,ko,0,0,110,,침울한 코지로이오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.17,TitleEP,en,0,0,233,,That's Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:23.17,TitleEP,en,0,0,110,,Depressed Kojiro
Comment: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,計画の進み具合はどうですかな、卑弥呼殿。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,계획의 진행 상태는 어떻습니까, 히미코 님.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:30.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ms. Himiko, how is the plan going?
Comment: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:36.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ご安心を、半蔵殿。万事順調に住んでおります。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:36.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안심하세요, 한조 님. 모든 것이 순조롭게 진행되고 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:36.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not worry, Mr. Hanzo. Everything is going well.
Comment: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それはよかった。しかし、油断は禁物ですぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그건 잘 되었군요. 그렇지만 방심하면 안 됩니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:40.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,That is good to know. But do not let your guards down.
Comment: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.60,Default,ja,0,0,0,,千姫一行のことですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.60,Default,ko,0,0,0,,센히메 일행 말입니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.60,Default,en,0,0,0,,You mean Senhime and others?
Comment: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:49.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,心配ご無用。すでに刺客を送ってございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:49.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정하실 필요 없습니다. 이미 자객을 보내 두었습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:49.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to worry. I already sent an assassin.
Comment: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さすがわ、卑弥呼殿。手回しのよいことだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 히미코 님입니다. 용의주도하시군요.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's Ms. Himiko I know. How careful of you.
Comment: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵！もう行くわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 이제 간다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! We're leaving!
Comment: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,早く上がってきなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,빨리 올라와!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come here soon!
Comment: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってほしいダス！おいら、今新しい技を特訓してるんだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐 기다리시오! 나 지금 새 기술을 훈련하고 있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:37.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Just a moment-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'm now training for a new technique-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:42.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、海が敵だとしたら、お前の命などいくらあっても足りないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:42.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 바다가 적이라면 네 목숨이 몇이고 있어도 부족하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:42.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph! If your enemy is the sea, then no matter how many lives you have, they won't be enough!
Comment: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이오?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:43.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵、お前の剣は間合いが甘いのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 네 칼은 짬이 부족하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:47.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, your sword lacks distance!
Comment: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,間合いってなんだすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,짬이 뭣이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,What about distance-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:58.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,バカ目。そんなことも知らないのか。敵との距離を測ることだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:58.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,바보 놈. 그런 것도 모르냐! 적과의 거리를 재는 것 말이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:58.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't you know that?! You have to measure distance between you and your enemy!
Comment: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,バカとはなんだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,바보는 뭣이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,What was that idiot for-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いいか、見ていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠냐, 봐라!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Look and learn!
Comment: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、これが間合いだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥. 이게 짬이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph. This is how distance should be.
Comment: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、そんな長い刀だったらどんなに遠くの敵だって届くダス！そんなのじっともえらくないです！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 그런 긴 칼이라면 얼마나 멀리 있는 적이라도 쉽게 닿소! 그런 거 하나도 안 잘났소!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph! With a sword that long, no matter how far the enemy is, targeting is easi-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! That's not at all great-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何を？！私の剣を馬鹿にするのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭣이?! 내 칼을 무시하는 거냐?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:27.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! Are you looking down of my sword?!
Comment: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.71,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だったらどうだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 어떠오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.71,Default,en,0,0,0,, Then what-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:30.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,許さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:30.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서 못 한다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:30.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Comment: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:43.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっと！二人ともやめなさいよ。やるんだったら不知火一族を退治してからしてよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:43.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐! 둘 다 그만둬. 할 거라면 시라누이 일족을 퇴치하고 해!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:43.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop it, you two. If you're going to do it, then do it after you have dealt with Shiranui Clan!
Comment: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:48.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうでした。私たちは大事な仕事の途中でした。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:48.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그랬습니다. 저희는 중요한 일을 하던 도중이었습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:48.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,You are right. We were in the middle of an important job.
Comment: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.80,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんな奴に私の剣の素晴らしさを説明しても無駄というもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저런 놈에게 제 검의 대단함을 설명하는 건 소용 없습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,It is no use to explain the awesomeness of my sword to a guy like that.
Comment: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,向きになった自分が恥ずかしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,화낸 제가 부끄럽습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am embarrassed of myself for getting worked up.
Comment: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、待つだす！逃げるのは秘境だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오! 달아나는 건 비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.62,0:05:00.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop right there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Running away is cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いい加減にしなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,작작 좀 해!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,KNOW WHEN TO STOP!
Comment: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:05.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir...
Comment: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵、コジロー、千姫様でございますね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 코지로, 센히메 님이시죠?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, Kojiro and Senhime, right?
Comment: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,私はサイゴー様の使いのもんでございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저는 사이고 님의 심부름꾼입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a messenger of Mr. Saigo.
Comment: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.70,Default,ja,0,0,0,,サイゴーさんがあたしたちに何の用かしら。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사이고 씨가 제게 무슨 일일까요.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,What does Mr. Saigo have with us?
Comment: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:26.79,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい、サイゴー様は日夜不知火一族と戦っていらっしゃるお三方の労をねぎらうために、お食事を用意してお待ちでございます。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:26.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예, 사이고 님은 주야장천 시라누이 일족과 싸우고 계시는 세 분의 수고를 덜어드리기 위해 식사를 준비해 기다리고 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:26.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Saigo has prepared a meal to thank all your efforts to deal with Shiranui Clan.
Comment: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？オ食事⁉うわ、いくだす、いくだす！すぐいくだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 식사?! 우와, 가오, 가오, 바로 가오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! Meal?! Yes, we're going-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, we're going-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, we're going right now-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! 
Comment: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:37.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こりゃ、武蔵！見苦しいぞ！いったい、お前が食べ物のことで目の色を変えるときは、ろくなことがないのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:37.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,임마, 무사시, 흉하다! 대체 네가 먹을 것 이야기만 듣고 눈 색이 바뀌면 제대로 할 줄 아는 게 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:37.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, how unsightly of you! Whenever you hear about food, your eye changes, and you can't do anything right!
Comment: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,응, 응!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Comment: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:43.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなこと言っても、せっかく用意して待ってくれってるって言ってのに、断ったら悪いじゃないだすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:43.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 소릴 해도, 기껏 준비해서 기다리시고 계시는데, 거절하면 안 되오!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:43.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still, he went through all the trouble to prepare a meal for us, and we can't refuse that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇네.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's right.
Comment: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ぜひともお願いいたします。～きないと私が力でまっす。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꼭 부탁드립니다. 오지 않으시면 제가 야단맞습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:49.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please do so. If you don't, then I'll be scolded.
Comment: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、お言葉に甘えていきましょうか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 말하신 대로 가 볼까!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then let's go, as he told!
Comment: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やっただす！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 됐소!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:53.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yay-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:02.10,Note,ja,0,0,0,,サイゴー
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:02.10,Note,ko,0,0,0,,사이고
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:02.10,Note,en,0,0,0,,Saigo
Comment: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こちらで。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여기로.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,This way.
Comment: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:08.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あらあら、さすが一国の主ともなると、立派なとこに住んでるんだすな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:08.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이야, 역시 일국의 주인이라더니 대단한 곳에 살고 있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:08.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,An owner of a country sure lives in a great place-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ようこそ。武蔵、コジロー、千姫様。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,환영합니다. 무사시, 코지로, 센히메 님.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:19.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Welcome, Musashi, Kojiro, and Senhime.
Comment: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.06,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うわ、サイゴーさん！今日はいっぱい食べる来ただすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우와, 사이고 씨! 오늘은 잔뜩 먹으러 왔소!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Mr. Saigo! We're here to eat a lot today-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本日、お招きいただいて恐縮です。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오늘은 불러 주셔서 깊히 감사드립니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us to a meal.
Comment: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:34.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いえいえ、いごろ不知火一族と戦っていらっしゃる皆さんのご苦労を思えば、それぐらい何のこともありませんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:34.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니아니, 계속 시라누이 일족과 싸워 주시는 여러분의 수고를 생각한다면, 이 정도는 아무것도 아닙니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:34.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, no, to think about all your hard work of fighting against Shiranui Clan, this is nothing.
Comment: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さ、奥へどうぞ。どうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 안으로 들어오세요, 오세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please come in, come in!
Comment: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はいだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すごいダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,대단하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:46.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's awesome-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:52.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さつま揚げのステーキにさつま揚げのお刺身、さつま揚げのサラダにさつま揚げのプディング。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:52.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사츠마아게 스테이크에 사츠마아게 회, 사츠마아게 샐러드에 사츠마아게 푸딩.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:52.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Satsumaage steak, Satsumaage sashimi,\NSatsumaage salad, and Satsumaage pudding.
Comment: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:57.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ここにあるのは全部九州の名産、さつま揚げで作ってあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:57.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여기에 있는 건 전부 규슈의 명물 사츠마아게로 만들어져 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:57.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Everything here is made of Satsumaage, the local specialty of Kyushu.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、存分に食べてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 원하는 만큼 드세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please eat as much as you want.
Comment: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いただきます！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 먹겠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:01.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Comment: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맛있소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:04.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's tasty!
Comment: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなにがつがつ食べないでよ。みっともないじゃないの。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇게 걸신들린 듯 먹지 마! 꼴불견이야, 정말!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't eat so greedily! That is so unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:10.30,Note,ko,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,480)\fn@Malgun Gothic\frz281.2\bord2\fs36\an5\4c&H3D36B3&\c&H6AB9EB&\pos(605,232)}꺼억
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:10.30,Note,en,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,480)\bord2\fs36\an5\4c&H3D36B3&\c&H6AB9EB&\frz15.41\pos(598,227)}BURP
Comment: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなこと言ったって、どれもこれもうまいんだから仕方がないダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 소릴 들어도, 이것도 저것도 맛있으니 어쩔 수가 없소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:14.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,No matter what you say, everything's so tasty and I can't help myself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,恥ずかしくてとっても食べる気が起きないわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부끄러워서 먹을 생각이 없어진다...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,He's embarassing me to the extent that I lost my appetite...
Comment: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなことおっしゃらずに、さあ、お二人とも食べてください。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 소리 하시지 마시고 자, 둘 다 어서 드세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, and please eat, you two.
Comment: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ところで、シロはどうしたのですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런데 시로는 어디 있습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,By the way, where is Shiro?
Comment: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,シロ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,시로?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:26.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,Shiro?
Comment: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いつも連れていらっしゃる犬のシロです。姿が見えませんが。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,언제나 데리고 다시니는 개, 시로 말입니다. 모습이 안 보입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:31.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,The dog you always take along. I can't see him.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:38.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、シロですか。あ、シロはちょっと具合が悪くて犬小屋に寝かせています。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:38.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 시로 말입니까. 음, 시로는 좀 상태가 안 좋아서 개집에서 자게 하고 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:38.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean that Shiro! Er, Shiro isn't feeling so good, so he's sleeping in his dog house.
Comment: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:42.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それはいけない。どれ、私がお見舞いに行ってましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:42.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그건 안 됐네요. 어디, 제가 상태를 보러 다녀오겠습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:42.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's too bad. Let me go and take a look myself.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:48.08,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いえいえ、それには及びません。さあ、どうか食事のほうを。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:48.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니아니, 그러시면 안 됩니다. 자, 어쨌든 드세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:48.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, no, please don't do that. Please eat for now.
Comment: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どうしてそんない食事を急がすのですか。おんのちょっと様子を見てくるだけです。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 그렇게 식사를 서두르시는 것입니까? 저는 단지 모습을 보고 오려는 것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:53.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why are you so hurrying with the meal? I am just trying to take a look.
Comment: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そ、それは。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:55.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,T- that's...
Comment: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー、そんなに根掘り葉掘り聞いちゃ失礼よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로, 그렇게 시시콜콜 캐어물으면 실례야.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro, asking persistently like that is rude.
Comment: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.59,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あたしたちもいただきましょう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우리도 먹자.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let's eat, too.
Comment: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、がっついて食べるから喉を詰まらせる如。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저런, 급하게 먹으니까 목에 걸리는 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:12.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,It got stuck to your throat because you were so hurrying!
Comment: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、違うだす。体がしびれて。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아니오. 몸이 저려와서...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, that isn't it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. My body is getting numb...
Comment: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:18.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi!
Comment: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この症状は。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 증상은...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,This symptom...
Comment: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やはり毒だ。サイゴーさん、これはどういうことです！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 독이다. 사이고 씨, 이건 뭡니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is poisonous. Mr. Saigo, what's the meaning of this?!
Comment: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,くそ、あと一歩で三人まとめて殺せたものを。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 조금만 더 있었으면 셋 다 죽였을 것을.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, you three should already have been dead by now!
Comment: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,食い意地のはってやつのおかげで、だいのしになってしまったわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,식탐부리는 놈 덕분에 밝혀져 버렸구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:36.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,That glutton got everything discovered!
Comment: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だれだ、貴様！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,누구냐, 네놈은!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:37.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Who are you bastard?!
Comment: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:47.10,NoteOnAnime,ja,0,0,0,,クマソン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:47.31,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,50,,쿠마손
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:47.10,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,50,,Kumason
Comment: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,俺は不知火一族のしかた、クマ殺しのクマソンよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.64,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(쿠마: 곰)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.64,Note,en,0,0,0,,(Kuma: bear)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 시라누이 일족의 자객, 곰 죽이는 쿠마손이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am an assassin of Shiranui Clan, Kumason for bear-killing!
Comment: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:53.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ、この程度の罠にはまるとは、口ほどにもないやつらよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:53.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,헤, 이 정도의 함정에 걸리다니 보잘것 없는 놈들이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:53.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Heh, falling into a trap like this would probably mean you are nothing great.
Comment: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:59.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、罠だということは知っていったさ。ただお前たちの手掛かりがほしくて、だまされた～をしていたのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:59.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 함정이라는 건 알고 있었다. 단지 네놈들에 관한 실마리를 원해서 속은 척 했을 뿐이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:59.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph! I knew this was a trap! I just played along with you because I wanted clues about you bastards!
Comment: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんで教えてくれなかっただす。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 안 알려줬소...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.19,Default,ja,0,0,0,,教える前にお前ががつがつ食べてしまったんじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,말해주기 전에 네가 막 쳐먹었잖냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:06.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,You already ate it all before I tell you!
Comment: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:17.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、クマソン！お前たちのアジトを教えてもらおうか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:17.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 쿠마손! 네놈들의 아지트를 알아야겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:17.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kumason! I will have to know where your hideout is!
Comment: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ、なかなかやるんじゃないか。お前ら、下がっていろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 하는 놈이군. 너희들은 빠져 있어라.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see you're pretty confident. You guys can stay back.
Comment: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こいつは俺様が料理してやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 놈은 내가 요리해 주겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'll cook this guy up.
Comment: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:29.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ふん、この私にそんな短い刀で向かってくるのか。愚かな。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:29.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 이 내게 그런 짧은 칼로 대들다니 멍청하긴.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:29.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph. Fighting me with such short swords? How foolish.
Comment: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.34,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,꽤 하는구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're pretty good!
Comment: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:56.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ、俺様のパンチは一発でクマを倒す威力があるのだ。さあ、今度は逃がさないから覚悟しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:56.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,헤, 내 펀치는 한방으로 곰을 쓰러트리는 위력이 있다. 자, 이번엔 못 피할 테니 각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:56.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Heh, my punch is enough to take a bear down with only one punch! You won't get away this time, so be prepared!
Comment: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:04.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それは私のセリフだ。お前の技はすべて見切った！今度、私の前に入ったときがお前の倒れる時だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:04.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그건 내가 할 말이다! 네 기술은 전부 확인했다! 이번에 내 앞에 왔을 때야말로 네가 쓰러지는 때다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:04.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's my line! I checked out all your techniques! As soon as you appear in front of me, you're going down!
Comment: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もらった！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잡았다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,I got you!
Comment: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:11.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:11.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐야?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:11.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:20.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ、いいこと教えてやろう。俺様はクマ殺しのクマソンと呼ばれてるが、もう一つの名を。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:20.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋은 거 알려주지. 난 곰 잡는 쿠마손이라고 불리는데, 또 하나의 이름이 있지.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:20.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let me tell you something. I am known for bear-killing Kumason, but I am known for an another name.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.03,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刀折りのクマソンと呼ばれているんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼 부러뜨리는 쿠마손이라고도 불리지!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:24.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am called sword-breaking Kumason!
Comment: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,私も物干竿が！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 모노호시자오가!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:28.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,My Monohoshizao!
Comment: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:35.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー、なんごくらすな、変わって武芸者がいるで～だす。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:35.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:35.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:41.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなのんきなこと言ってる場合じゃないでしょ？このままじゃコジローが殺されちゃう！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:41.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 느긋한 소리 하고 있을 때가 아니잖아? 이대로라면 코지로가 살해당할 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:41.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is not the time for that! Kojiro's gonna be killed at this rate!
Comment: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんだ～だす。しびれて仕方ないダス。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もう！肝心な時にちっとも役に立たないんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,진짜! 중요한 때에는 전혀 도움이 안 된다니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really, you aren't being helpful whenever we need!
Comment: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:55.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,毒消し飲んで早く元気になりなさい！これだけ飲めばすぐに聞くでしょ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:55.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,해독제 삼키고 어서 건강해져! 이만큼 먹었으면 바로 듣겠지!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:55.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Swallow these antidotes and become healthy! You'll become good soon by overdosing!
Comment: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ほらほらほらほら！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이랴이랴이랴이랴!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Swallow it! Just swallow it!
Comment: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おかしいダス。体が勝手に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이상하오. 몸이 멋대로...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is not right-{\i1}dasu{\i0}. My body is...
Comment: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんでもいいから早く行きなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,됐으니까 어서 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:02.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Just go already!
Comment: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Comment: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.53,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、めざわりな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에잇, 눈에 거슬리는 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お前に～ないだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:11.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助けてほしいダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,도와주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.24,Default,ja,0,0,0,,助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help!
Comment: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,へ、バカ目。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,헤, 멍청한 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Heh, that fool.
Comment: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵、コジロー！今のうちに逃げるわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 코지로, 이 틈을 타 도망치자!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Kojiro! Let's run away using this chance!
Comment: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:44.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:44.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.10,0:11:44.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro!
Comment: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,私の刀。。。物干竿が。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 칼이... 모노호시자오가...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:50.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,My sword... My Monohoshizao...
Comment: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何言ってんのよ、コジロー！早く来なさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐 하고 있어, 코지로?! 어서 와!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Kojiro?! Come already!
Comment: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.27,Default,ja,0,0,0,,待って、こりゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라, 이 자식들아!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop right there, you bastards!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,くそ！追え！一人も逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장! 쫒아라! 하나도 못 빠져나가게 해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn! Get them! Do not let even one get away!
Comment: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,強敵クマソンを相手に、武蔵達の勝機はあるのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,강적 쿠마손을 상대로 무사시 일행에게 승리란 가능한가?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:20.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Is it possible for Musashi and others to defeat Kumason, a powerful enemy?
Comment: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.42,Default,ja,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤のご飯を待って！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:23.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for the stormy latter half!
Comment: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.40,Eyecatch,ja,0,0,0,,EC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.40,Eyecatch,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 검호전 무사시 로드
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.40,Eyecatch,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Kengouden: Musashi Road
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:28.40,Eyecatch,,0,0,0,,{\an2}by Subdivers
Comment: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.74,Note,ja,0,0,0,,めざせ　ジパングの星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.74,Note,ko,0,0,0,,노려라 지팡구의 별
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.74,Note,en,0,0,0,,Become Jipangu's Star
Comment: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、むなしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 덧없도다.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,How fruitless it was.
Comment: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あのつらくて苦しい修行の日々が、なんだったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 괴롭고 고통수러운 수련의 날들은 무엇이었는가.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,What were the painful and tormenting days of training for?
Comment: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いたくだん、おはりなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,203, 들어와!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:46.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,203, come in!
Comment: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あれ、～も入れてよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어, 나도 들어갈래!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, let me join!
Comment: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.36,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だめだ、お前！そんなにききずって足でまといでて！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.36,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 돼, 너! 그렇게 발만 질질 끌면 걸려!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can't! You're gonna trip since you always drag your feet!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いこういこう！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,가자, 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Comment: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ、待てよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 기다려!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Comment: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:05.23,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー。お前はジパングの輝けるみょうじょうにならなければいけないのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:05.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로. 너는 지팡구의 빛나는 금성이 되어야 한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:05.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro. You have to become the bright Venus of Jipangu.
Comment: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,泣くな！くじけるな！～しばれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,울지 마라! 꺾이지 마라! 훈련해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't cry! Don't lose heart! Train!
Comment: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:09.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Comment: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.43,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー。お父様のような立派な武芸者になるのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로. 아버지와 같은 훌륭한 무예자가 되세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:18.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro, become a splendid martial artist like your father.
Comment: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:35.76,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ごめん！ゆるせよ！こりゃ！ごめんなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:35.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안! 용서해 줘! 제발! 미안해!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:35.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry! Please forgive me! Please! I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,来る日も来る日も、つらい修行の毎日だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,매일매일 쓰라린 수련의 연속이었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,Day after day, it was an endless pain.
Comment: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そして、
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,And...
Comment: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,해냈다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it!
Comment: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,この時から、燕のしっぽは二つに割れるようになった。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 때부터 제비의 꼬리는 둘로 갈리게 되었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:57.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,Swallows' tails are split ever since then.
Comment: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.45,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え、と、言われている。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,음, 고 전해진다.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:59.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Well, that's the folklore.
Comment: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:07.51,Default,ja,0,0,0,,長く苦しい時も共に過ごした物干竿、どうして折れてしまったのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:07.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기나긴 쓰라린 시간 동안 함께 지낸 모노호시자오. 어떻게 부러져 버렸는가...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:07.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,How did my Monohoshizao end up being broken, after being together for all the long and painful time?
Comment: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジローたら、すっかり落ち込んじゃってるわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로도 참, 정말 큰일났어.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:16.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro's feeling so down...
Comment: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.11,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ひどい目にあった出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,끔찍한 일을 당했소...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was terrible-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,クマソンのやつ、このおらをたっぷりさせてもらう出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쿠마손 놈, 이 나를 힘들게 만들었소...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:21.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,That Kumason bastard made me suffer so much-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:27.21,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ちょっと、武蔵！もとあといえばみんなあんたが悪いんだからね。何とかしなさいよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:27.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐, 무사시! 애초에 죄다 네 잘못이잖아! 뭐라도 해 봐!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:27.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, Musashi! It's all your fault, at the first place! Do something!
Comment: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.17,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？なんでおいらが悪いんだすか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 왜 내 탓이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Why is this my fault?
Comment: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:35.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武芸者のくせに独入りの料理なんか食べて、しびれていたのがいけないのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:35.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무예자 주제에 독 들어간 요리 따위 먹고 마비된 게 잘못된 거야!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:35.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Being paralyzed by eating poisonous food is wrong, for a martial artist!
Comment: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.63,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:36.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,No way!
Comment: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんか文句あるの？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 불만 있냐?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:38.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Any complaints?!
Comment: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.10,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いい？絶対コジローを元に戻しなさいよね！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠어? 반드시 코지로를 원래대로 돌려 놔.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,You will restore Kojiro, or else!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:46.25,Default,ja,0,0,0,,でも、どうやって戻したらいいか、おいら、さっぱりわからないだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:46.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도, 어떻게 돌려놓을지 나 전혀 모르겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:46.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,But I don't know how to restore him at all-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？コジローがいないんだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라? 코지로가 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Kojiro isn't there-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？どこ行った出すか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에? 어디 갔소?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where did he go-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.81,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あ！自殺するつもりだわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아! 자살할 생각이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! He's going to take suicide!
Comment: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.67,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いけんだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안돼오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:14:59.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,He can't-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー！・コジロー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-코지로!\N-코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Kojiro!\N-Kojiro!
Comment: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ば、バカな真似はやめるダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,바, 바보같은 짓은 안 되오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.45,0:15:05.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,D- don't be a fool-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:10.52,Default,ja,0,0,0,,放してくれ。愛刀をなくした今の私は、もう生きていても仕方がないんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:10.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이거 놔라. 애도를 잃은 지금의 내게는 더 이상 살아있을 방도가 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:10.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let me go. I do not worth living anymore since I lost my beloved sword!
Comment: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.28,Default,ja,0,0,0,,何を～だすか。刀なんて、また手に入れればいいんじゃないだすか！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 소리이오. 칼 따위는 다시 손에 넣으면 되오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you saying-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?! You can get an another sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:22.16,Default,ja,0,0,0,,～は～してくれ。あれほど長い刀、そう簡単に手に入らないの。私が一番よく知っているのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:22.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모르는 소리 마라. 그 정도로 긴 칼, 그렇게 쉽게 손에 넣을 수 없는 건 내가 제일 잘 안다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:22.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,You don't know a thing! I know the best that it is difficult to obtain a sword that long!
Comment: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.77,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あきらめてはいけないだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,포기하면 안 되오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,You must not give up-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.22,Default,ja,0,0,0,,死んだら花見ができなくなるだす。探せばきっと見つかるだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죽으면 꽃놀이 못하게 되오. 찾으면 분명 찾을 수 있을 것이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:32.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can't enjoy flowers if you die-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! If we try to find one, then we'll find one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.46,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵。。。お前っていいやつだな。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시... 너 좋은 놈이구나...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi... You are a good guy...
Comment: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんかやるみくいだすな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\i1}왠지 잘 한 것 같소.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think that I did a good job-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どうだ！見つけたか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떠냐! 찾았냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Report! Did you find them?!
Comment: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,八方手を尽くしておりますが、まだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,팔방으로 손을 뻗치고 있습니다만 아직입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're searching everywhere possible, but not yet.
Comment: 0,0:15:54.07,0:16:00.09,Default,ja,0,0,0,,えい、早く見つけ出せ！俺様のパンチは連中を倒したくてうずうずうーずしているのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:16:00.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에잇, 어서 찾아내라! 내 손은 그 놈들을 쓰러트리고 싶어 불끈불끈부울끈하고 있단 말이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:16:00.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dammit! Go find them already! My hand is bursting into rage and flaaaaaaaaaring up, wanting to take them down!
Comment: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.92,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんな長い刀、うちにはおいてありませんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.92,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇겐 긴 칼, 저희에겐 없네요.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.92,Default,en,0,0,0,,We don't have any sword that long.
Comment: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,見たことありませんね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,본 적 없네요...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,I never saw one...
Comment: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,いや、そんなの見つけんのは無理ですわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 그렇게 긴 걸 찾는 건 무리에요.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Finding one that long is almost impossible.
Comment: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.68,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あるわけないでしょ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,있을 리가 없지요.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's no way those would even exist.
Comment: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ありますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:24.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,We have one.
Comment: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.18,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本当か？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말인가?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really?!
Comment: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,南蛮到来の刀なんですが、これなんてどうです？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.84,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(남만: 동남아 및 그곳에 식민지를 가진 나라 - 스페인, 포르투갈 등)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.84,Note,en,0,0,0,,(Southern {\i1}barbarian{\i0}: SE. Asia, sometimes including Spain and Portugal, for having colonies there)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,남만에서 도래한 칼입니다만 이걸로 어떻나요?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:29.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's a sword introduced by Southern barbarians. Would this suit your needs?
Comment: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、ずいぶん頼りないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,음, 별로 믿음직스럽지가 않구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Er, it doesn't look so dependable...
Comment: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そんなことありません！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럴 리 없습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,No way!
Comment: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どうする？このままじゃコジローはいつまでも落ち込みっぱなしよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩌냐? 이대로는 코지로는 앞으로도 쭉 침울해 있을 거야.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:49.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,What should we do? Kojiro will be keep feeling down at this rate.
Comment: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうだ！こうなったらおいらが刀を作ってやるだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇소! 이렇게 된 바 내가 칼을 만들어 주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:54.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's it! I'll make a sword for him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.75,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？武蔵に作れるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 무사시 만들 수 있어?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really? Can you make one, Musashi?
Comment: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.84,Default,ja,0,0,0,,任せるダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,맡겨 두시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:16:58.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Leave it to me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.86,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい！できた出す。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여기! 다 됐소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:00.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here! It's done-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これが刀か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이게 칼이냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sword, eh?
Comment: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.58,Default,ja,0,0,0,,さあ、使ってみるダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 써 보시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Try using it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,どう出す？使いのこっちは！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻소? 쓴 소감은?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,How do you feel-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うん、まぁまぁだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,응, 꽤 괜찮구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Erm, good enough, I guess.
Comment: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.73,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵！刃がないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 칼날이 없잖냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Blades are missing!
Comment: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.38,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あら？どこ行っただす？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라? 어디 갔소?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Where did they go?
Comment: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.90,Default,ja,0,0,0,,刃ならここにあるわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼날이라면 여기 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,You can find the blades here!
Comment: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おせんちゃん、大丈夫だすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,센짱, 괜찮소?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sen-chan, are you alright-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:39.41,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なんてものを作るのよ！あたしが運動神経がよくて、かわいかったからよかったものの！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:39.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭘 만든 거야! 내가 운동 신경이 좋아서, 귀여워서 다행이었던 것을!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.26,0:17:39.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,What kind of contraption did you make?! Be thankful that I have a good reaction, and I'm cute!
Comment: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,普通の人だったら死んでいたわよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일반인이었다면 죽었다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,An usual person would have already died!
Comment: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.96,Default,ja,0,0,0,,か、かわいいのがどういう関係があるだすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,귀, 귀여운 게 뭔 관계이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,H- how does being cute have something to do with it-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.01,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おやめください、千姫様。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그만하세요, 센히메 님.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please stop, Senhime.
Comment: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.56,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵も、私のためを思ってやってくれたのです。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시도 절 위해 해 준 것입니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi did that for me.
Comment: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.94,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お二人の、私を思う気持ちｈに茹れて、コジロー、目が覚めました。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,둘이서 절 위하는 걸 보고 이 코지로, 눈을 떴습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:56.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,I finally realized after you two were doing all that for me.
Comment: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.88,Default,ja,0,0,0,,本当？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Really?
Comment: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,はい。これからは刀の長さにはこだわりません。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예. 지금부터는 칼의 길이에는 연연하지 않습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:02.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes. I won't be particular about the length of sword from now on.
Comment: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.93,Default,ja,0,0,0,,くそくらえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,똥이나 먹어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}eat shit!
Comment: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,だめだ。間合いが取れない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,틀렸어. 짬이 닿지 않아...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:20.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's no good. It can't make to the distance...
Comment: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:25.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,ああ、コジローのやつ、また落ち込んでしまっただす。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:25.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 코지로 놈, 또 침울해졌소.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:25.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,That Kojiro became down again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.04,Default,ja,0,0,0,,困ったわね。どこかに物干竿に代わりような長い刀がないのかしら。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,곤란하네. 어디에 모노호시자오만큼이나 긴 칼 없을까...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,This is bad. I wonder if there's a long sword that compares to Monohoshizao...
Comment: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.95,Default,ja,0,0,0,,あり申す。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,있소이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:32.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,There exists one.
Comment: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:37.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,げ、サイゴーさん！いや、クマソン！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:37.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어, 사이고 씨! 아니, 쿠마손!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:37.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?! Mr. Saigo! No, Kumason!
Comment: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.57,Default,ja,0,0,0,,な、またサイゴーさんに化けてきたダスか？だけど、もうだまされないダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어차피 또 사이고 씨로 변장해 왔겠소! 그렇지만 더는 속지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:43.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,You came here disguised as Mr. Saigo again! We won't be fooled again!
Comment: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:53.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お？何を言ってるのでごわす。おいどんは不知火一族と戦っている武蔵君たちに礼をつけてもらおうと食事を誘いに来ただけでごわすよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:53.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 뭔 소리요. 나는 시라누이 일족과 싸우고 있는 무사시 군 일행에게 감사의 표시로 식사를 대접하고자 했을 뿐이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:53.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hm? What are you talking about-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}? I was just offering you a meal, for fighting hard against Shiranui Clan-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,その通り、名物のさつま揚げもたくさん買ってきたでごわす。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 만큼 명물인 사츠마아게도 잔뜩 사 왔소이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,And since that, I bought a handful of Satsumaage-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:06.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,げげ？！いくらおいらでももうさつま揚げには引っかかれないダス！サイゴーさん、いや、クマソン！覚悟！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:06.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐?! 아무리 나라고 해도 더는 사츠마아게에는 걸려들지 않소! 사이고 씨, 아니, 쿠마손! 각오하시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:06.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! Even for me, I won't be fooled to Satsumaages again-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Mr. Saigo, prepare yourself-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.54,Default,ja,0,0,0,,チェスト！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,체스트!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chest!
