Comment: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.65,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こんな大声出せるのは間違いなく本物だす。。。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이런 큰 목소리를 내는 걸 보니 틀림없이 진짜이오...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,Judging by that big voice of yours, you are real one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Comment: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.62,Default,ja,0,0,0,,そうだったでごわすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그랬구려.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.91,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それでおいどんをそのクマソンとかいうものと間違えたでごわすか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래서 날 그 쿠마손이란 놈으로 착각한 것이구려!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,So that's why you confused me with that Kumason guy-{\i1}gowasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.44,Default,ja,0,0,0,,すまんだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.31,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それでサイゴーさん、さっき言ってた長い刀って、どこにあるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래서 사이고 씨, 아까 말한 긴 칼 어디에 있어?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:41.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,So, Mr. Saigo, where is that long sword you told us about?
Comment: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,アマクサ島にあるでごわす。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아마쿠사 섬에 있소.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's at Amakusa Island.
Comment: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.13,Default,ja,0,0,0,,天草島？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아마쿠사 섬?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:46.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Amakusa Island?
Comment: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:54.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,天草島にはコジローどんの刀よりも長い、伝説の秘剣があるといううわさでごわす。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:54.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아마쿠사 섬에는 코지로 님의 칼보다도 긴 전설의 비검이 있는 듯 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:54.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that there is a legendary secret sword that is even longer than Mr. Kojiro's sword.
Comment: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.12,Default,ja,0,0,0,,それをとってくればいいダスな！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그걸 가져오면 되겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then we'll go take that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!\N
Comment: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.47,Default,ja,0,0,0,,天草島へは行かせんぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아마쿠사 섬에는 못 간다.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will not let you go to Amakusa Island.
Comment: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.07,Default,ja,0,0,0,,げ、クマソン！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쿠마손!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kumason!
Comment: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:13.14,Default,ja,0,0,0,,お前らに天草島に行かれると面倒なるんだ。ここで死んでもらうぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:13.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너희들이 아마쿠사 섬에 가면 귀찮아진다. 이곳에서 죽어줘야겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:13.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Things will get complicated if you go to Amakusa Island. You'd better die here!
Comment: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,今度は負けないダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이번엔 안 지오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:16.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't lose this time-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.74,Default,ja,0,0,0,,死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죽어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:17.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,Die!
Comment: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.49,Default,ja,0,0,0,,死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죽어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,Die!
Comment: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.97,Default,ja,0,0,0,,うわ、ずるいだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아니, 치사하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's cunning-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しね！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죽어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Die!
Comment: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.98,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー、しっかりしてよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로, 정신 차려!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:29.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro, get a grip!
Comment: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.40,Default,ja,0,0,0,,これじゃどっちがボディガードかわからないじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이래선 누가 보디가드인지 모르잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:35.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now we don't know who is whose bodyguard!
Comment: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.55,Default,ja,0,0,0,,チェスト！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,체스트!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chest!
Comment: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.30,Default,ja,0,0,0,,見申したか！示現流、～術の威力を。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘들 봤겠지. 지겐류 기합술의 위력을.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,I hope all of you saw Jigen Style Shout Technique!
Comment: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.83,Default,ja,0,0,0,,え？千姫様！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.83,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 센히메 님!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.83,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Senhime!
Comment: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:55.64,Default,ja,0,0,0,,こ、今度はもう少し小さな声でやってよね。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:55.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다, 다음엔 좀만 더 작은 목소리로 해 줘...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:55.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,P- please do it with a smaller voice next time...
Comment: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もう逃げられんぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이제 못 도망간다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,You won't run away this time!
Comment: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,逃げてばかりじゃ無いダス！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,도망갈 뿐만이 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't just run away-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Comment: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.72,Default,ja,0,0,0,,他愛もない。お前の刀も折ってやる。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.72,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사리 분별이 안 되는군. 네 칼도 부러뜨려 주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.96,0:21:15.72,Default,en,0,0,0,,How guileless of you. Let me break your sword too!
Comment: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.33,Default,ja,0,0,0,,おいらの刀は一本だけじゃないんだす！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.33,Default,ko,0,0,0,,내 칼은 하나뿐만이 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:19.33,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have more than one sword!
Comment: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.39,Default,ja,0,0,0,,なに？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐야?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:30.82,Default,ja,0,0,0,,接近戦を～ところ～同じことよ。これでもくらえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:30.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,접근전을 안 할 생각이라도 마찬가지다! 이거라도 먹어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:30.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,Even if you're not up for a close combat, there's no difference! Take this instead!
Comment: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.37,Default,ja,0,0,0,,もう一度くらえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,한번 더 먹어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Take it once again!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,二天一流、閃光剣！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이천일류 섬광검!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nitenichiryu: Flash Sword!
Comment: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.32,Default,ja,0,0,0,,コジロー。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:03.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojiro.
Comment: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:09.02,Default,ja,0,0,0,,恐るべき不知火一族の刺客、クマソンは倒した。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:09.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무서운 시라누이 일족의 자객 쿠마손은 쓰러트렸다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:09.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,They managed to take down Kumason, a frightful assassin from Shiranui Clan.
Comment: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.66,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、愛刀を折られたコジローはすっかり落ち込んでしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 애도가 부러진 코지로는 아주 침울해지고 말았다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:13.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,But having his beloved sword broken, Kojiro was deeply disheartened.
Comment: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:22.15,Default,ja,0,0,0,,武蔵は、この永遠のライバルを立ち直らせることができるのか。そして天草島に隠された秘密とは！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:22.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 이 영원의 라이벌을 재기시켜줄 수 있을까? 그리고 아마쿠사 섬에 숨겨진 비밀이라?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:22.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will Musashi managed to recover Kojiro, his eternal rival? And what is that secret hidden in Amakusa Island?
Comment: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.48,Default,ja,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤の次回を待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.48,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 다음 이야기를 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.48,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for the stormy next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.32,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,허공의 주머니에 달이
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.32,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:46.58,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,뛰어넘어가는 일도 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:46.58,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.96,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,큰 소리로 웃으면
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.79,0:22:48.96,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:51.59,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,내일에는 아침이 와
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.58,0:22:51.59,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:56.92,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,잃는 것 따위는 아무것도 아니야
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:56.92,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:00.51,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,계속 해나가! 앞으로 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.92,0:23:00.51,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep going! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:02.93,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,맨손은 강해
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:02.93,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:13.02,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:13.02,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:21.07,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,인생 그런 거야! 기회가 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:21.07,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:25.79,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,꼬리를 흔들며 쫒아와!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:25.79,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:36.71,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:36.71,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:45.18,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,미래도 그런 거야! 내일이 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:45.18,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how the future is, too! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:51.02,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,양손을 벌리고 웃고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:51.02,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Comment: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.99,Default,ja,0,0,0,,物干竿を折られたコジローは落ち込みっぱらし。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.99,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모노호시자오가 부러진 코지로는 완전 침울해졌소.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.41,0:24:06.99,Default,en,0,0,0,,For having his Monohoshizao broken, Kojiro is really feeling down.
Comment: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:11.85,Default,ja,0,0,0,,仕方なく、おいらはサイゴーさんのいった伝説の秘剣を探しに天草島へ。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:11.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어쩔 수 없이 나는 사이고 씨가 알려준 전설의 비검을 찾기 위해 아마쿠사 섬에!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.41,0:24:11.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,I had no choice but to go to Amakusa Island that Mr. Saigo told me about, to find the legendary secret sword!
Comment: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:16.29,Default,ja,0,0,0,,しかし、その刀は持つにふさわしいものでなければ抜くことができないんだす。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:16.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 그 칼은 가질 자격이 있는 자만이 빼들 수 있다고 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:16.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,But, they say that only the ones who are qualified can pull out the sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Comment: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.05,Default,ja,0,0,0,,たえして、コジローの燕返しはよみがえるのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,과연 코지로의 츠바메가에시는 되살아나는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Will Kojiro's Tsubamegaeshi be revived?!
Comment: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:23.35,Default,ja,0,0,0,,次回、今よみがえる伝説の剣だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:23.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 지금 되살아나는 전설의 검이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:23.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! The Reviving Legendary Sword!
Comment: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:26.69,Default,ja,0,0,0,,疾風怒濤の天草島だす！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:26.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 아마쿠사 섬이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:26.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's the stormy Amakusa Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,NoteOnAnime,ko,60,0,60,,{\an7}다음 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,TitleEP,ko,0,0,225,,지금 되살아나는
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,TitleEP,ko,0,0,110,,전설의 검이오
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}재미있게 보세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,NoteOnAnime,en,60,0,60,,{\an7}Next Story
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,TitleEP,en,0,0,225,,The Reviving
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,TitleEP,en,0,0,110,,Legendary Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.93,0:24:29.90,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}We hope you enjoy!
